A W.I.T.C.H. (woman in total control of her self) in her natural element 🥰🏔🔮 Aaaand here’s the cap on @colourthetrails Colour the Slopes Summit in @revelstoke! I went Dec 7-12 as a speaker, passionate @colourthetrails community member, and lover of all snow sports.

Let’s also acknowledge @jujumil, who continues to leave me inspired with every interaction. Her story, and the more you get to know the tribulations and triumphs that have defined her journey to and within community organizing, make her work that much more incredible. While navigating lateral harm and exploitation of Black, Indigenous, racialized people within and alongside our communities, Juju has maintained the most admirable levels of compassion and dedication amid significant personal costs. We are so, so lucky for everything you do for US. And thank youuuu @neverbadtimeforchanges for being the support she needs to continue being what she is to us and more ♥️♥️♥️

