Today was a long day of presenting at AESP (an energy conference) in New Orleans, & the power radiating from the love, intention, and brilliance of these @indi_city earrings really did translate to my presence on stage and in these sometimes draining contexts.

I cannot recommend @indi_city more genuinely… ✨✨✨

F is for friends who do stuff together, U is for you and meee, N is for n’ywhere and n’ytime at all down here in the deep blue sea 🎶

@diversenaturecollective it’s about time we got together!!! Follow follow follow for amazing outdoor programming and opportunities in Ontario 🥾

@wildroga the most refreshingly unique approach to yoga and wellness I’ve witnessed 😂♥️ LOVE what Ro is putting out into this world. If you are ever seeking wellness programming at your gathering, I highly recommend hitting her up!

@efefruci literally a goddess in a devine human host.

@tayvieeee made me these beautiful earrings and shared bits of herself with me that made me feel so inspired, loved, and thankful. 

Keeping up my numba 1 spot as best third wheel around 😂 I actually love @alyssamcdo @quaidjohnston and everything they do… you’ll see their work all over my page in the coming months when they go more public about it 👀

Everything my spirit needed last weekend was found in the home that @boner.tz is to me, and the magic that happens when @boner.tz @zherbach and I get back together. These are the people that truly appreciate the journey. We been through it since high school.

@ethnicsnax stinging nettle, wasps, the tour de duck, giant fungi… we SURVIVED 😂

