I can tell everyone I work with “I love you.” And with these faces, and these people, how can you not ♥️

Getting team portraits has been a dream since we all got together to share @ancestorsfuture with the world in 2020. As a small social enterprise that began in the rumblings of the COVID-19 pandemic, our retreat was the first time we’ve physically all been in the same room.

We brought @feather.photo in to capture our team portraits. While he’s clearly known for his studio shots (with travelling set up!), his outdoor portraits hit HARD too💥 We’ll share more of those in the new year.

